PATENT NOTICE
=============

Patent Pending — US Provisional Patent Application No. 63/993,589
Filed: February 28, 2026
Inventor: Manish Kumar

PrismOS and its core architectures are protected by a pending United States
patent. The following inventions are covered:

  • Spectrum Graph™ — Multi-dimensional spectral knowledge representation
    A novel graph database where every node carries 7 spectral dimensions
    (cognitive, emotional, temporal, social, creative, analytical, physical)
    that evolve over time.

  • Refractive Core™ — Intent refraction through spectral analysis
    An AI reasoning engine that "refracts" user intent through the Spectrum
    Graph to produce contextually rich, personalized responses via multi-agent
    collaboration.

  • You-Port™ — Encrypted personality migration with graph merge/diff
    Encrypted state migration for carrying an AI personality across devices
    with graph merge, diff, and conflict resolution.


